HE9kEdZaMAADLIU?format=jpg&name=large","line":15,"embedded":true},{"title":"图像","target":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HE9kQaYbIAAtxQL?format=jpg&name=large","line":41,"embedded":true},{"title":"图像","target":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HE9k0dDbcAAIbTG?format=jpg&name=large","line":69,"embedded":true},{"title":"图像","target":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HE9lTKkakAAMu-A?format=jpg&name=large","line":122,"embedded":true},{"title":"S-001 MotherDuck Obsidian RAG","target":"S-001 MotherDuck Obsidian RAG","line":137},{"title":"C-042 RAG","target":"C-042 RAG","line":138},{"title":"图像","target":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HE9lveObMAAN8zu?format=jpg&name=large","line":177,"embedded":true},{"title":"《如何基于 Obsidian 和 Claude 打造 AI 时代超级大脑？》","target":"https://x.com/yanhua1010/status/2020342019575673223?s=20","line":219},{"title":"《Obsidian + Claude Code：你的笔记库就是你最强大的 AI 上下文》","target":"https://x.com/yanhua1010/status/2029369274847072591?s=20","line":220},{"title":"《我用 Podwise 把播客变成了可检索的知识库》","target":"https://x.com/yanhua1010/status/2033726054351966613?s=20","line":221},{"title":"@yanhua1010","target":"https://x.com/@yanhua1010","line":225}],"metadata":{"title":"用 LLM + Obsidian 构建个人知识库：基于 Karpathy 的“LLM Knowledge Bases”工作流","source":"https://x.com/yanhua1010/article/2039966047378583815","author":["[[Yanhua (@yanhua1010)]]"],"published":"2026-04-03","created":"2026-04-04","description":"Karpathy 今天发了一条推文，讲他怎么用 LLM 构建和管理个人知识库。我反复读了几遍。不是因为什么新概念，是因为他做的事和我这几个月在 Obsidian 里瞎折腾的东西，结构上撞了。但他用了一个词来概括，我之前一直没找到：编译（Compile）。把原始资料\"编译\"成结构化...","tags":["#ai-workflow","#to-process"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[[47,57],[75,94],[132,155]],"key":"8-Raw/x-clippings/用 LLM + Obsidian 构建个人知识库：基于 Karpathy 的“LLM Knowledge Bases”工作流.md"},
